original_title: Cheech Marin & Friends: Live from South Beach
overview: Legendary King of Latino Comedy guy Richard 'Cheech' Marin hosts a unforgettable night of non-stop laughs with five up-and-coming comedians: Al Madrigal,Gilbert Esquivel, Carlos Oscar, Felipe Esparza and Joey Medina.
title: Cheech Marin & Friends: Live from South Beach
